 my onli joke thank to a professor at the univers of manitoba circa number set in the old west a cowboy is ride along on his favorit hors when he sudden surround and taken prison by a band of roam indian the indian take the cowboy and his hors and tell him the tradit way that the tribe deal with their victim each day for the next number day you get a wish if it in our power to grant it to you we will after the number wish is done you die a horribl slow death time for your first wish the cowboy think a bit and say "i want to talk to my horse." so the indian bring the hors over the cowboy whisper in his ear and the hors run off a littl while later the hors come back with a beauti blond nake woman the cowboy and the woman go in the tent appropri nois are heard and then the hors take the woman away the next day time for the wish come and the indian amaz at yesterday perform all gather round the cowboy say "i want to talk to my horse" so the hors is brought over the cowboy whisper in it ear and the hors take off a littl while later the hors come back with a beauti brunett nake same routin as befor cowboy and the women go in the tent ... etc on the third and final day the indian are total amaz and are eager to hear what the cowboy wish will be so they all gather round and the cowboy again say "i want to talk to my horse." the hors is brought over and this time the cowboy grab the hors by the head stare right at him and say -- "read my lip -- poss posse!" owen URL